Experiment 7: Widget Application
Aim
To design and develop a simple widget-based application using basic UI components (such as Button, TextView, EditText, etc.) and perform actions based on user interaction.

Algorithm
1. Start the program
2. Initialize the application interface (UI)
3. Add required widgets such as:
    TextView (for displaying text)
    EditText (for user input)
    Button (for performing action)
4. Set properties for each widget (text, size, layout, etc.)
5. Wait for user interaction
6. When Button is clicked:
   Read input from EditText
   Process the input (e.g., display message or perform calculation)
7. Display the result in TextView or Toast message
8. Repeat steps for further interaction if needed
9. Stop the program
